title: How's BENJAMIN Doing?
body_text:
Text messages were sent out on midday, July 28, to each and every full-time
EastCoastDodgeball
warrior:
"'MoneyMaker' Rimshot Contest returns at DB 150! Check website later in the week for more as well as a second bombshell announcement!
That's right! Following the success of DODGEBALL C30, DODGEBALL 150 will have it's own cash giveaway pregame contest featuring players and spectators! And as the text indicates, a second announcement regarding DODGEBALL 150 will be made public right here on
dodgeball.livejournal.com
later this week.
body_html:
Text messages were sent out on midday, July 28, to each and every full-time EastCoastDodgeball warrior: "'MoneyMaker' Rimshot Contest returns at DB 150! Check website later in the week for more as well as a second bombshell announcement!


That's right! Following the success of DODGEBALL C30, DODGEBALL 150 will have it's own cash giveaway pregame contest featuring players and spectators! And as the text indicates, a second announcement regarding DODGEBALL 150 will be made public right here on dodgeball.livejournal.com later this week.
